  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> are around 24m² and sleep two to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed)</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> are around 35m² and sleep up to five people. There is one room with a double bed and an additional smaller bedroom with bunk beds</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are around 12.5m² and have an ensuite with shower</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Kettle</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. CHF 5.50 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged 11 and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Steps into property:<strong> 2</strong></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
